content: There is a board on the Seongjagak Seogye and the Winter Woldae. Usually the king bows in a space with three sides of the front of the pavilion, and it is estimated that in the Joseon dynasty he bowed on this board.
There is also a cafe nearby, a great place to come and take a walk with children and play ㅎㅎㅎ
It's good to take a light walk with children. After climbing Morak Mountain, you can come down to the park.
